# ChackTok

ChackTok is a commercial photo booth software platform built for professional event operators and rental businesses.

It enables automated capture, processing, and delivery of photos and videos in high-frequency event environments, supporting scalable commercial deployments worldwide.

---

## What We Do

- Commercial photo booth software
- Event imaging and media automation
- Workflow management for rental and event businesses
- Hardware integration and system-level control

---

## Who It’s For

- Event rental companies
- Photo booth operators
- System integrators
- Hardware partners in the event industry

